  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️ IMPORTANT WARNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>X-POINT IS NOT A CASUAL GAME.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is <strong>no simplified tutorial</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>no quick victories</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is <strong>no “press a button - get fun”</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mistakes have consequences</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are not ready to <strong>study</strong>, <strong>read</strong>, <strong>analyze</strong>, and <strong>learn from your own failures</strong> - <strong>please do not buy this game</strong>.<br><br>❌ WHAT THIS GAME DOES NOT OFFER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To avoid false expectations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a shooter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> an arcade game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a “15-minute session” game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> beginner-friendly software</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a relaxation product</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are used to games adapting to you - X-POINT will not.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✔️ WHO THIS GAME IS FOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-POINT is created <strong>exclusively</strong> for players who enjoy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >studying complex systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >finding solutions independently</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >making irreversible strategic decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >understanding mechanics instead of pressing buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >playing games that <strong>do not try to please everyone</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get satisfaction from <strong>the process of understanding</strong>, not instant reward — you are in the right place.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧪 PROJECT PHILOSOPHY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-POINT does not try to be convenient.<br>Does not try to be friendly.<br>Does not try to appeal to everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>deliberately niche game</strong>, created for a limited audience that values depth over accessibility.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️ IMPORTANT WARNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>X-POINT IS NOT A CASUAL GAME.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is <strong>no simplified tutorial</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>no quick victories</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is <strong>no “press a button - get fun”</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mistakes have consequences</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are not ready to <strong>study</strong>, <strong>read</strong>, <strong>analyze</strong>, and <strong>learn from your own failures</strong> - <strong>please do not buy this game</strong>.<br><br>❌ WHAT THIS GAME DOES NOT OFFER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To avoid false expectations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a shooter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> an arcade game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a “15-minute session” game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> beginner-friendly software</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ this is <strong>not</strong> a relaxation product</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are used to games adapting to you - X-POINT will not.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✔️ WHO THIS GAME IS FOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-POINT is created <strong>exclusively</strong> for players who enjoy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >studying complex systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >finding solutions independently</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >making irreversible strategic decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >understanding mechanics instead of pressing buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >playing games that <strong>do not try to please everyone</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get satisfaction from <strong>the process of understanding</strong>, not instant reward — you are in the right place.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧪 PROJECT PHILOSOPHY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-POINT does not try to be convenient.<br>Does not try to be friendly.<br>Does not try to appeal to everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>deliberately niche game</strong>, created for a limited audience that values depth over accessibility.</p>",
